A2: Agent 2
A3: Agent 3

USR -> API: Create swarm
API -> HH: Decompose goal
HH -> API: Subtask list {
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}
API -> DB: Store tasks (multiple)
API -> USR: Swarm created {
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}
A1 -> DB: Claim Task A
A2 -> DB: Claim Task B
A1 -> DB: Complete A
DB -> A3: C unblocked {
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}
A3 -> DB: Claim C
A2 -> DB: Complete B
A3 -> DB: Complete C

